  <brief_title>Uncemented Compared to Cemented Femoral Stems in Total Hip Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <acronym>CHANCE</acronym>
  <official_title>Study of Prosthesis Choice in Older Patients With a Dislocated Femoral Neck Fracture of the Hip</official_title>
